# Walkthrough: Portkey Content Templates

## Overview
The overarching goal was to upgrade the `portkey-content-engine` resources. 
- **Phase 1**: Deeply research Portkey AI's features and improve the 7 content templates. 
- **Phase 2**: Research the latest 2025/2026 Portkey news and inject these trending topics directly into the Week 1 execution plan.
- **Phase 3**: Upgrade [DEVRAL_SKILL.md](file:///d:/Work/cli/temp/portkey-content-engine/DEVRAL_SKILL.md) to strictly enforce step-by-step, template-driven content generation for future AI agents.

## Actions Taken

1. **Research & Documentation:** 
   We successfully conducted a deep web search on Portkey AI's documentation and created a structured research document ([portkey-docs-research.md](file:///d:/Work/cli/temp/portkey-content-engine/portkey-docs-research.md)). The research focused on the core pillars of the platform: AI Gateway & Routing, Prompt Management, Observability & Tracing, and Guardrails.

2. **Template Review & Updates:** 
   We analyzed and systematically updated all 7 markdown templates in the `templates/` folder to incorporate Prompt Management and Observability use cases. 

