- **LinkedIn Post Template ([linkedin-post-template.md](file:///d:/Work/cli/temp/portkey-content-engine/templates/linkedin-post-template.md))**:
  - Added two powerful "Hook Formulas" specifically targeting the pain points of hardcoding prompts and "flying blind" on LLM costs in production.

- **Programming Guide Template ([programming-guide-template.md](file:///d:/Work/cli/temp/portkey-content-engine/templates/programming-guide-template.md))**:
