- **Tweet Thread Template ([tweet-thread-template.md](file:///d:/Work/cli/temp/portkey-content-engine/templates/tweet-thread-template.md))**:
  - Added a "Prompt Versioning" viral hook pattern ("Stop checking prompts into git.").
  - Added a Python code snippet specifically designed for tweet screenshots, demonstrating zero-code prompt execution.

